description: Amazing Hotels: Life Beyond the Lobby Series 1 Travel Documentary hosted by Giles Coren and Monica Galetti, published by BBC in 2017 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/9/92/Amazing-Hotels-Life-Beyond-the-Lobby-Series-1-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Amazing Hotels: Life Beyond the Lobby Giles Coren and Monica Galetti roll up their sleeves to work alongside staff in some of the most extraordinary hotels across the globe. 2) Mashpi Lodge Ecuador Giles Coren and Monica Galetti head to the Andean Cloud Forest of Ecuador to work at Mashpi Lodge, a $10-million modernist hotel featuring an extraordinary gondola cable car that 'flies' guests one mile through the jungle canopy at a dizzying height.
